Backend (PowerShell, from d:\Internship\backend):


cd backend
python -m venv .venv          # first time only
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt   # first time only
$env:DB_ENGINE = "sqlite"
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
API will be at http://localhost:8000/api/.

Frontend (separate terminal, from d:\Internship\frontend):


cd frontend
npm install   # first time only
npm run dev
App will be at http://localhost:5173, already configured via frontend/.env to call the API at http://localhost:8000/api.